### 3. Instructions for Manual Setup

Now, follow these steps exactly in your terminal.

**1. Create the Project and Navigate Into It:**

First, create the main project folder and all the nested directories. You can do this manually or by running these commands in your terminal:

```bash
mkdir -p recruitment-management-system/public recruitment-management-system/src/{api,app,assets/images,assets/styles,components/{common,layout},features/{auth,dashboard},hooks,pages,routes,services,utils}
cd recruitment-management-system